---
title: Mushroom, Bacon & Herby Potato Filo Galette with Basil Pesto & Mixed Salad
description: When you put in the hard yards you want to be able to show off your creation and nothing looks as impressive as a
filo pastry galette. Everyone will ‘ooh’ and ‘ahh’ at the mushrooms, bacon and leek topped with fresh basil pesto. It’s a stellar standout that will earn you admiration and praise!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6604d632faa50670154dc0c0-d5496bbe.jpeg
